default-
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThe technology can create new risks, including new forms of crime, that are not adequately covered by existing
default laws – the need for regulation 
defaultofdefault technology.
default 
defaultTh
defaultis also includes debates on whether the mere perception of risk, e.g. by the wide
defaultr
default population or by insurance companies, merits to create legal reassurances 
defaultthat are not objectively justified.
defaultEmerging legal
default issues of AVs can be
default-
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultSpecific to the car and the car industry (example 
defaulte.g. the definition of 
default “fitness to  drive”)
default-
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultGeneric  issues created by autonomous technologies (example: applicability of 
defaultlegal 
defaultterms such as
default 
