default“malicious intent” to machines)
default-
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultImported from other technological fields, e.g emerging legal issues of internet law that affect the communication of the car with a base station (example: possible data retention duties for car manufacturers/sellers)
defaultAs alwa
defaultys, legal issues can arise on the subnational (devolved), national and international including EU) level. 
defaultFrom a UK perspective, this means that future pressures on the UK legal system  can be caused by
default-
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultDevelopments in the technology
default and the needs of the U
defaultK car manufacturers
default-
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultIndividual events that create pressure to act (
defaulte.g. 
defaultan accident with fatalities)
default-
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultFuture reactions of international bodies and organisations to these developments
default 
default over which the UK has some, but no full control (e.g.  changes to the 
defaultGen
defaulteva 
default Convention; EU initiatives to prevent market fragmentation)
default-
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultManufacturing  developments in other countries that affect 
default UK law 
defaultthrough the legal framework of the WTO (e.g. US car makers arguing that UK safety rules are a trade barrier
default, or that the abs
defaultence of a suitable legal framework is inherently a protectionist measure)
defaultFinally, the degree of legal changes 
defaultthat is 
defaultneeded will obviously depend 
defaulto
defaultn the degree of autonomy and the fun
defaultctionality embedded in the car – ranging from merely assistive technolo
defaultgies to self-driving cars with a human driver 
default 
default“in the loop” to the vision of the fully automated car 
defaultthat like a chauffeur drops 
defaultits owner 
default off at 
defaulthis 
default destination and then drives itself home. 
defaultLegal issues can combine 
defaultissues across 
defaultall of the above parameters, creating a large number of  very heterogeneous 
defaultproblems
default, that make considerable demands on the expertise needed to address them. 
defaultTo give some impression of the diversity of the issues that can come up, 
default3
default examples
default, from opposing
default ends of the spectrum
default, all of which with uncertain legal answers and the 
