default 
default1)
defaultA challenge at the WTO that UK regulation on the safety standards for 
defaultAVs 
defaultare unreasonable given the developments in technology and therefore discrim
defaultinate
default against US manufacturers
default. 
default2) A driver is accused of murdering his wife with his car. The main evidence comes from 2 on
default-
default board sensors of the car, which operate independently, but whose inputs are processed by the same 
defaultcentral 
defaultcomputer
default unit on the ca
defaultr
default. Are these two piece
defaults
default of evidence and the corroboration requirement of Scot criminal law is fulfilled, or is it a single piece of evidence that still needs corroborating?
default3) Due to a known bug in the car’s software, 
defaulta vulnerability
default is created that allows
default third parties to hack into a car’s computer system and steal personal information for fraudulent purposes. During a hack, the performance of the other software systems is degraded, and as a result the system reacted 
defaulttoo 
defaultslowly
default. 
defaultThe driver
default, relying
default on his 
defaultsoftware, 
defaultdoes not
default intervene even if he could hav
defaulte. An accident follows
